This is a well written and acted movie with a lot of funny moments. Kim Chiu  is absolutely gorgeous. One of my favorite parts were the interviews of different couples married for various lengths of time, they were very funny and moving and showed you what true love is all about. I also liked the movies theme song sung by Yeng Constantino. Highly recommend this movie.
